UI_NewGame_Tip_BattleHard_Content:
Determines complexity of combat AI. Affects the level of strength and strategy of the enemies in battle.
<color=#E3C66DFF>(The higher the difficulty, the stronger the enemies will be;
The more intelligent the enemies will be;
The more actions they will perform in battle.
For example: they will have better control of the distance and timing for attack and defense.)
(Note that difficulty names actually represent how hard they are. If you're a new player it's recommended to choose the "Difficult" difficulty.)</color>

